{"arkId":"cl010361740","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010361740","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"vase","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Ancien titre","value":"Trois pi\u00e8ces de c\u00e9ramique de Suse (non inventori\u00e9es au d\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales)"},{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"vase"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : Suse I (-4000 - -3500)","currentLocation":"Toronto (Canada), Royal Ontario Museum","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":-4000,"endYear":-3500,"imprecision":"","text":"Suse I","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"A 7952","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"L947.2.3","type":"Num\u00e9ro d\u00e9positaire"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"coupe\r\n\r\nD\u00e9cor : chevron ; chien ; troupeau ; flots\r\nPr\u00e9cision sur l\u0027objet : Coupe \u00e9vas\u00e9e, reposant sur un pied annulaire peint. Diam\u00e8tre maximal irr\u00e9gulier. \r\nD\u00e9cor g\u00e9om\u00e9trique \u00e0 composition bipartite : deux r\u00e9seaux de trois lignes bris\u00e9es d\u00e9corent l\u0027int\u00e9rieur de la coupe et forment deux profondes indentations accueillant de chaque c\u00f4t\u00e9 un animal-peigne \u00e0 t\u00eate recourb\u00e9e et un d\u00e9cor de chevrons inclus dans un rectangle. Dans le champ, de part et d\u0027autre d\u0027une croix de Malte inscrite dans un cercle concentrique et une ligne ondul\u00e9e, deux autres animaux-peigne \u00e0 t\u00eate recourb\u00e9e et deux ensembles de chevrons \u00e9galement inscrits au coeur d\u0027un rectangle. Sur le bord interne, un filet noir (et motifs de dents de loup) laisse s\u0027\u00e9chapper des groupes de hachures. \r\nLa tranche externe du pied et la l\u00e8vre sont soulign\u00e9s par un trait de peinture.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"8,3","displayDimension":"8,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"20,8","displayDimension":"20,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : terre cuite (beige (Munsell 5Y7\/2))\r\nTechnique : peinture (brune)","placeOfCreation":"Suse","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"Suse","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Morgan, Jacques Jean Marie de","note":"","role":", Fouilleur\/Arch\u00e9ologue"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"partage apr\u00e8s fouilles","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1908","startYear":1908,"endYear":1908}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","longTermLoanTo":"Royal Ontario Museum, Toronto","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"partage apr\u00e8s fouilles"}],"denomination":[{"value":"vase"}],"material":[{"value":"terre cuite"}],"technic":[{"value":"peinture"}],"description":[{"value":"chien"},{"value":"troupeau"},{"value":"chevron"},{"value":"coupe"},{"value":"flots"}],"place":[{"value":"Suse"}]},"bibliography":[],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/0000000021\/0000361740\/0000515570_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000361740\/0000515570_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2013 Mus\u00e9e du Louvre \/ D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","type":"","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/0000000021\/0000361740\/0000515568_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/ca